Hi!


The configuration process produces a bogus signames.h file under linux
1.3.6. The file /usr/include/linux/signal.h used to extract the signal
names just includes /usr/include/asm/signal.h under 1.3.x. 

Using /usr/include/asm/signal.h fixes the problem.

tom

